Processing Fees

CP

March 9, 2018

1: SUMMARY

  • As % of Processed Revenues slight overall increase, but the Chargeback and Failed fees remained constant;

  • Historically over two FY there is a significant increase in the *number of Chargeback transactions from mobile devices;

2: Share of REVENUES

Processing fees by Transaction Type as percentage of overall Processed REVENUES (cc SALES+REBILLS)

  • Overall increase of transaction fees to 7.4%, mainly on mobile and unidentified device types;

  • Chargeback fees remained flat from JAN at 1.4%;

  • Failed transaction fees remained flat at the lowest level over two fiscal years
